{"tid":678980,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)黃飛鴻1-4","createTime":"2018-05-26T13:25:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T18:51:26.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"472f8a5c2104b35d858e24b5926023e687f6adb7","tid":678980,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T13:25:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=WX5OTyccEgu%2Fcnu9sobLfdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=d96ab719\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=WX5OTyccEgu%2Fcnu9sobLfdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=4f55fa80\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=WX5OTyccEgu%2Fcnu9sobLfdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=226ee11d\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/b1/Once_Upon_a_Time_in_China.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fb1%2FOnce_Upon_a_Time_in_China.jpg&h=40eed523&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/yz4OSgZmMChsWlGe04mdBw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/nownews.com/4338ea1fdd8260dbf86681277e178f0f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fyz4OSgZmMChsWlGe04mdBw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fnownews.com%2F4338ea1fdd8260dbf86681277e178f0f&h=07f13d7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.清朝末年，中國正在進行洋務運動，西風東漸，洋槍威力直迫練武之士。黑旗軍教頭黃飛鴻，為廣東十虎之一，武功高強。關東高手嚴振東，因為籍籍無名，而致生活潦倒，為了揚名立萬，挑戰黃飛鴻被拒，嚴振東砸爛寶芝林招牌，引致盛傳黃飛鴻被嚴振東擊敗。一日偶遇少筠，鐵釘寬一見鍾情，與為黃飛鴻頓變成情敵，遂拜嚴振東為師。後來，少筠誤中積善先生詭計，被拐往美國當娼妓。鐵釘寬欲救，被嚴振東痛打，黃飛鴻帶牙擦蘇、豬肉榮、凌雲楷飛馳而至。黃飛鴻與嚴振東展開一場激戰&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n2.黃飛鴻應國際醫學會的邀請，與梁寬、少筠前往廣州，因緣際會結識孫文和陸皓東。白蓮教利用神佛之說，宣揚神功刀槍不入，扶清滅洋，火燒西洋學校，黃飛鴻不滿白蓮教殘害無辜出手相救，更替學生四處奔走，後來得到陸皓東的幫助，寄居英國領事館。滿清提督納蘭元述為了對付裡頭窩藏的革命黨人，不惜協助白蓮教圍攻領事館，孫文早已先行脫逃，黃飛鴻與喬裝弟子的陸皓東以阻止白蓮教教徒肆虐為由、脫離納蘭元述掌握，直搗朝天觀擊敗九宮真人，揭破神功秘密。在護送陸皓東回頭取革命黨員名冊時，遇上納蘭元述的追捕，陸皓東傷重不治，黃飛鴻遂與其展開生死戰&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n3.黃飛鴻到京師探望父親黃麒英，卻得知俄國人要在舞獅獅王大賽時刺殺宰相李鴻章，黃飛鴻雖不喜歡李鴻章，卻為了民族大義，還是決定出手相救。最後，黃飛鴻在舞獅獅王大賽中，打敗了惡棍趙天霸，也乘機拯救了李鴻章<br />\n<br />\n4.1993:黃飛鴻設館 &quot;寶芝林&quot; 授徒，拜入 &quot;寶芝林&quot; 門下的人與日俱增。黃感地方不夠使用，命牙擦蘇另覓新地方開分館。蘇奉命往河南覓新址，途中遇上黃飛虎。虎十分崇拜黃，得知蘇來意，便主動幫忙，用美人計令蘇答允買下虎所介紹之地方作為&ldquo;寶芝林&rdquo;分館，而分館則與虎所開的妓院 &quot;香芝館&quot; 為鄰&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n9 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=WX5OTyccEgu%2Fcnu9sobLfdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=3cbbfa15\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=WX5OTyccEgu%2Fcnu9sobLfdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=8a8280a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e77e844199f517d949157e47ea31d8fd7680fa6","tid":678980,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T13:26:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abbcce8e1d623897931c713a4152578e389ad8f5","tid":678980,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T13:40:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c92444383dc1d2b93c85766c2d5b639e74274af","tid":678980,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T14:10:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"826d9877a4c715a56d4504000f40ad46c21d1a5f","tid":678980,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T15:43:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81d1f8459f55ebd9ebed6ba1db1a867e059b2a85","tid":678980,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T16:53:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b348738ca63871736f13585af5b83aa4883ad744","tid":678980,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T18:51:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}